 cannot be unity.
 In any case, using the coefficients from the previous problem yields
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(x_{n})=\left(\frac{dx}{dt}\right)_{x=x_{n}}=\frac{1}{\Delta t}\left[\frac{3}{2}x_{n}-2x_{n-1}+\frac{1}{2}x_{n-2}\right]+O(\Delta t^{2}),
