\begin_inset Formula $\partial S$
\end_inset

.
 In particular, letting 
\begin_inset Formula $z=-.5$
\end_inset

 gives 
\begin_inset Formula $0=4r^{2}-4r+1=(2r-1)^{2}$
\end_inset

, so that 
